<br>
The next expansion that has already been hinted at is the one including the underwater dungeon for LoIO.<br>
<br>
Frankly though, I would be very surprised if all the old content received a new revamp. <br>
<br>
I do see them doing some revamps though. One possible way for them to do something may be to &quot;Cazic Thule&quot; a couple of the older dungeons to allow a bit more content for the upper level players. From what I understand Plane of Hate is already revamped so i would expect a few more changes along those lines, instead of a wholesale revamp of entire zones.<br>
<br>
It is sad to see all the empty zones in the game these days but frankly, even if they were revamped i dont think that they will all turn overnight into the OS of old. Some of the dungeons were badly designed so people won't want to go there anyway, and a lot of the open zones, particularly some of the kunark ones, are a complete waste of space as well.<br>
